OBSwap is the most potential trading platform on the EOS chain, with features such as security, smoothness, simplicity, flexible fees, and friendly configuration.
It is specially designed for the project party to create its own trading pair. The project party can configure the trading transaction rate by itself, as well as designate the fee collection account, and the market making reward for the corresponding trading pair.

Launched on September 15th 2020, Vigor is a multi-asset, collateralized lending and borrowing protocol. Vigor allows you to borrow VIGOR stablecoin, backed by other crypto assets and to earn income on your crypto assets by lending them as insurance assets backing loans. Vigor also allows you to reduce your exposure to price volatility. Welcome to the future of Defi!

Launched on September 15th 2020 and in continuous operations Vigor Protocol is a multi-asset, self balancing, fully collateralized crypto lending and borrowing protocol. It is unique in all crypto as it adjusts for solvency autonomously based on its DAC member’s User interactions and the high speed data feed from the equally reliable Delphi Oracle soon to be releasing its new QED version. Vigor Protocols unique approach is impractical on any EVM blockchain and only feasible running on faster lower cost Antelope based Blockchains. There is no human intervention setting rates or forced liquidations by auction it’s smart contracts do all the work. The Protocol enables you to borrow VIGOR, a “low volatility” token, which is backed by your crypto assets and earn rewards. Vigor Protocol’s smart contracts are designed to mimic the European Union’s Solvency II Protocol. Vigor allows you to reduce your exposure to crypto price volatility. Welcome to the future of Defi, reDeFined.
